Package: griddb
Title: Standardized Global Grid System for Crop Simulation
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Pepe", "Clavijo", email = "pepe@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Provides tools to generate stable, globally-consistent grid
    cells for use as spatial simulation units in crop modeling workflows,
    along with supporting lookups for administrative boundaries and crop
    presence masks, backed by a PostGIS database.
